    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯释放美国记者，与克里姆林宫特工进行大规模交换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯释放了《华尔街日报》记者埃文·格什科维奇，并监禁了克里姆林宫的批评者，这是俄罗斯与西方几十年来最大规模的囚犯交换，以换取总统弗拉基米尔·普京寻找的一名重要刺客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默警告社交媒体公司注意其在英国暴力事件中扮演的角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/starmer-warns-social-media-firms-about-role-in-uk-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，英国极右翼示威者在全英国引发暴力骚乱，似乎是由网上虚假信息引发的。基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 警告社交媒体公司，犯罪就发生在“你们的场所”内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/starmer-warns-social-media-firms-about-role-in-uk-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:37:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
